TI  - DATA COLLECTION AND ANALYSIS PLATFORM CONSTRUCTION WITH DEEP LEARNING IN THE TOBACCO PRODUCTION PROCESS
T2  - APPLIED ECOLOGY AND ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH
